Architecture — SOC Stack
⦁	Kubernetes workloads (Falco, Kyverno, Trivy, CrowdSec, Wazuh Agents)
⦁	VM-based Security Onion for packet capture & Elastic dashboards
⦁	Central Wazuh Manager for agent data
⦁	Log pipeline forwards into Elastic/Kibana + Loki/Grafana
⦁	Alerts feed into SOC workflows (Discord/Slack webhooks, email, dashboards)
